{"tid":2157651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅昨到西藏 　稱當地安全穩定事關黨國發展大局","createTime":"2020-08-15T07:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T07:28:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0542d912aebff2abd5961312b8a5ac3dc1dc95b2","tid":2157651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543900-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543900-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8cLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=9daba582\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543900-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=672e53b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543900-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼外長王毅，昨日到西藏。<br />\n<br />\n外交部官網表示，王毅與西藏自治區黨委書記吳英杰等人座談時表示，西藏的安全穩定，事關黨和國家發展大局。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，面對世界百年變局和新型冠狀病毒疫情的複雜影響，外交戰線將與西藏的中共黨員一起，為確保國家安全和西藏長治久安，共同努力，為支持西藏對外開放合作、推動經濟社會發展，作出應有貢獻。"},{"pid":"39e3dd3835a9494714f993d0f953c6cfc0f82467","tid":2157651,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"王毅除咗刷鞋仲識做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/03173744/image1504431388263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F03173744%2Fimage1504431388263.png&h=dff5d13b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}